		<td class=bod>
			<center>	
			This page was last updated 14 July 2000.
			</center>

			<p align=justify> 
			This is the complete list of all of my current projects.  I've
			compiled all of them with 
			<a href="http://msdn.microsoft.com/vstudio/">MS Visual C++</a>,
			using the <a href="http://sunsite.auc.dk/allegro/wip.html">
			3.9.32 WIP of Allegro</a>.  If you don't know how where to
			start with the Visual Studio, look at 
			<a href="http://members.xoom.com/dynasta/allegro_tutorial/index.html">
			James Johnson's Allegro/MSVC Tutorial</a>.
			</p>

			<p align=justify>
			You'll also need to make sure that you've got the current 
			dll to run the executables for these projects.  Here it is:
			<a href="./ald3932.dll">ald3932.dll</a>; or as a .zip file:
			<a href="./ald3932.zip">ald3932.zip</a>.
			</p>

			<p align=justify>
			On to the projects!
			</p>
		</td>
	</tr>
